{"tid":1564151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"邱局長，係咪食左偉哥，成日想插美國屎忽","createTime":"2019-09-12T16:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T16:06:44.000Z","uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"666593f03d6415c1a987d2b0918d70f2c74689f8","tid":1564151,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:03:25.000Z","msg":"商務及經濟發展局局長：我在以往多個場合亦有說過，香港的經貿地位其實是由《基本法》賦予。《基本法》第116及151條說明香港可作為高度自主的獨立關稅地區及貿易單位，亦賦予香港在世貿組織（世界貿易組織）內享有單獨成員的地位，因此本身這地位並非任何一個國家單方面的施予。<br />\n<br />\n　　我亦有留意美國國會最近有討論香港的情況，要求美國政府改變對香港的政策。在這方面，作為另一個政府，我不在此「搭嘴」，評論他們的工作。美國對香港的經貿政策一直都是源自其一九九二年的法案，該法案訂明香港若可維持高度自治，美國會維持對香港的政策，我相信這亦反映了美國自身在香港的利益。"},{"pid":"7dc7c2b37f5fb5c144cb06a2beb1da8f4aa49087","tid":1564151,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:03:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f113bdf7c0640e89035e84c149d2b3dd19323c6","tid":1564151,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:03:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"e46bbfeb96d365bf15d84cbafb978dcc55279265","tid":1564151,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:04:55.000Z","msg":"why don't request US to abolish policy act?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70659675360f683b8e01cddd2df1032677b50e1","tid":1564151,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}